    ExperimentEnricher, MIEnricher<Experiment>
    public class FullExperimentUpdater
extends FullExperimentEnricher
    Provides full update of experiment. - update minimal properties of experiment. See MinimalExperimentUpdater - update xrefs - update annotations - update confidences - update variable parameters
    Since:
    13/08/13
    Author:
    Gabriel Aldam (galdam@ebi.ac.uk)
